108 /* ----------------Configuration of the Cortex-M0 Processor and Core Peripherals---------------- */

119 /* ================================================================================ */
120 /* ================ Device Specific Peripheral Section ================ */
121 /* ================================================================================ */
122 /* Macro to modify desired bitfields of a register */
123 #define WR_REG(reg, mask, pos, val) reg = (((uint32_t)val << pos) & \
124  ((uint32_t)mask)) | \
125  (reg & ((uint32_t)~((uint32_t)mask)))
126 
127 /* Macro to modify desired bitfields of a register */
128 #define WR_REG_SIZE(reg, mask, pos, val, size) { \
129 uint##size##_t VAL1 = (uint##size##_t)((uint##size##_t)val << pos); \
130 uint##size##_t VAL2 = (uint##size##_t) (VAL1 & (uint##size##_t)mask); \
131 uint##size##_t VAL3 = (uint##size##_t)~((uint##size##_t)mask); \
132 uint##size##_t VAL4 = (uint##size##_t) ((uint##size##_t)reg & VAL3); \
133 reg = (uint##size##_t) (VAL2 | VAL4);\
134 }
135 
137 #define RD_REG(reg, mask, pos) (((uint32_t)reg & (uint32_t)mask) >> pos)
138 
140 #define RD_REG_SIZE(reg, mask, pos,size) ((uint##size##_t)(((uint32_t)reg & \
141  (uint32_t)mask) >> pos) )
142 
144 #define SET_BIT(reg, pos) (reg |= ((uint32_t)1<<pos))
145 
147 #define CLR_BIT(reg, pos) (reg = reg & (uint32_t)(~((uint32_t)1<<pos)) )
